articles.title: The Optimism about a Coronavirus Vaccine Is Misplaced
articles.description: Vaccines take time to develop and deploy. It won’t be any different for coronavirus.

articles.author: Tobias Hoonhout, Tobias Hoonhout
articles.title: Congress Agrees to $8.3 Billion Emergency Funding Bill to Combat Coronavirus
articles.description: Congressional leaders have agreed to pass an $8.3 billion emergency funding bill to combat the coronavirus outbreak, with the House expected to vote on the legislation Wednesday afternoon.

articles.title: Beijing Weighs Chinese Alternative to WHO in Response to Coronavirus Public Relations Disaster
articles.description: A state-sponsored Chinese think tank is evaluating international opinion on the formation of the country's own alternative to the World Health Organization.
